{
  "id": "adv_event_2109_01_05",
  "title": "The Last Chance",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next morning",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 0.8600000023841856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、今日の練習を始める前に\nお話ししたいことがあるんですけどいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ before we start today’s practice‚\nthere’s something I’d like to say‚ if you don’t mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.7,
      "endTime": 8.160526371002202,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "いいけど……改まってどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure. What’s the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.366666666666667,
      "endTime": 11.000000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 11.333333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "実は、莉央さんに怒られると思って\n今まで言えずにいたことがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you’d be angry with me if I said it‚\nso I’ve kept my lips sealed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.333333333333334,
      "endTime": 17.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 17.533333333333335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "私が怒るようなこと？　一体なんの話かしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something that would anger me? What are you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.533333333333335,
      "endTime": 21.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 21.866666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "……新曲の振り付けのことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s about the choreography of the new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.866666666666667,
      "endTime": 24.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "私は今の振り付けを変えるべきだと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think we should change the choreography we have.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.633333333333333,
      "endTime": 28.700000000000003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 29
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "私と葵が考えた振り付けに\n問題があると言いたいのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re saying there’s a problem with\nthe choreography Aoi and I created?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29,
      "endTime": 33.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "誤解しないで下さい！\nお二人が考えた振り付けは素晴らしいと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t get me wrong!\nI think the choreography you two thought up is great!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.56666666666667,
      "endTime": 38.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 33.5666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今回の曲にはもっと合うパフォーマンスが\nあると思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I think we could perform in a way that would match\nthis song a lot better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.166666666666664,
      "endTime": 45.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "……詳しく聞かせてもらえるかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could you tell us the details?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.766666666666666,
      "endTime": 47.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 45.7666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 48
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "私が一人で前に出て踊る部分がありますけど\nあそこは莉央さんも前に出るべきだと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s a place where I step forward alone to dance‚\nbut I think Rio-san should step forward too for that bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48,
      "endTime": 55.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 55.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "オリジナルメンバーの莉央さんと\n新メンバーの私が前に出て一緒に踊ることで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Rio-san‚ the original member‚ and me‚\nthe new member‚ step forward and dance together‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8,
      "endTime": 62.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 62.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "新生リズノワが歌うThe Last Chanceに\nふさわしい表現になると思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think that would be a suitable expression for the\nnew LizNoir singing The Last Chance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3,
      "endTime": 68.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 68.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そこはあなたがソロで踊る見せ場なのよ？\n自分の見せ場がなくなってもいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But isn’t that the place where you show off your solo dancing?\nYou don’t mind losing your own showcase?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 74.26923082302773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 74.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "構いません\n私はこの曲で妥協はしたくないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t mind.\nI don’t want to compromise this song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.56666666666666,
      "endTime": 78.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "これが新生LizNoirだと\n胸を張って言えるパフォーマンスにしたいんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If this is the newly reborn LizNoir‚\nI want to make it a performance I can be proud of.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1,
      "endTime": 83.93333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……愛がここまではっきり自分の意見を言うなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if you’re expressing your own opinion so clearly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 88.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 84.3666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "これも合宿の成果かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "because of this camp.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.9,
      "endTime": 90.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "いいわ、愛のアイデアを検討しましょう\n新しい振り付けを考えるから愛も手伝って頂戴",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ let’s consider your idea.\nI’ll think of the new choreography‚ so you come help too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.56666666666666,
      "endTime": 97.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 90.5666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 97.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！　ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-okay! Thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 100.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 101.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "礼には及ばないわ\n愛は当然のことをしたんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t have to thank me.\nYou only did what’s right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.1,
      "endTime": 105.30000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 105.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirが最高のパフォーマンスをするために\nこれからも思ったことは遠慮無く言いなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ don’t hesitate to bring up any ideas you have\nto give LizNoir the best performances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.56666666666666,
      "endTime": 110.93333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 111.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_05-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　分かりました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ understood!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3,
      "endTime": 113.43333333333332,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3600.0000000000086
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_suzvillastudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 114.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
